## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d4e47-286"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> 最初に区別する検索を実行します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4e47-286"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> performs a case-sensitive lookup first.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d4e47-287">失敗した場合、2 番目の検索が行われます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4e47-287">If it fails, a second case-insensitive search is made.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d4e47-288">メソッドをスロー、 `IndexOutOfRange` 0 から始まる列序数が見つからない場合に例外です。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4e47-288">The method throws an `IndexOutOfRange` exception if the zero-based column ordinal is not found.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d4e47-289"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> カタカナの全角区別されません。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4e47-289"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> is kana-width insensitive.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d4e47-290">呼び出す効率的ではありません序数に基づく参照は、名前による参照よりも効率的であるため<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A>ループ内で。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4e47-290">Because ordinal-based lookups are more efficient than named lookups, it is inefficient to call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> within a loop.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d4e47-291">代わりに、<xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A>とし、割り当て、ループ内の整数型の変数に結果を使用します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4e47-291">Instead, call <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> once and then assign the results to an integer variable for use within the loop.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="d4e47-292"><xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> メソッドの使用方法を次の例に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d4e47-292">The following example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.Data.OracleClient.OracleDataReader.GetOrdinal%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
```vb  
Public Sub ReadOracleData(ByVal connectionString As String)  
  
    Dim queryString As String = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders"  
    Dim connection As New OracleConnection(connectionString)  
    Dim command As New OracleCommand(queryString, connectionString)  
  
    connection.Open()  
  
    Dim reader As OracleDataReader = command.ExecuteReader()  
  
    Dim custIdCol As Integer = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID")  
  
    Do While reader.Read()  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol))  
    Loop  
  
    reader.Close()  
    connection.Close()  
End Sub  
```  
  
```csharp  
public void ReadOracleData(string connectionString)  
{  
    string queryString = "SELECT OrderID, CustomerID FROM Orders";  
    OracleConnection connection = new OracleConnection(connectionString);  
    OracleCommand command = new OracleCommand(queryString,connection);  
  
    connection.Open();  
    OracleDataReader reader = command.ExecuteReader();  
  
    int custIdCol = reader.GetOrdinal("CustomerID");  
  
    while (reader.Read())  
        Console.WriteLine("CustomerID = {0}", reader.GetString(custIdCol));  
  
    reader.Close();  
    connection.Close();  
}  
```
